The course introduces and teaches the classical dance training system, coordination, movement pattern, various stylistics, terminology, repertoire. The course will also focus on the development of ballet technique to dynamics.Objectives/eesmärkid:  - Obtain elementary practical and theoretical principles of ballet. -To develop already obtained steps, to learn the aesthetic principles and stylization, to be able to use it in contemporary dance. - Learn to apply physical capability, based on bodycognition experience, in ballet technique.Learning outcomes/õpiväljund:  -Knows how to target muscles and joints in ballet. - Possesses body awareness in ballet. - Knows the basic terminology of ballet and can verbalise them. - Knows the training methods of ballet and knows how to put them into practice.
